{"tid":2497051,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺巨人結局，個作者只係賣弄伏筆，劇情好幼稚  ？？？","createTime":"2021-04-20T08:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T09:40:18.000Z","uid":123335,"like":20,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"109b8a0a259df78ce87c8bfc2afbb93eff51522d","tid":2497051,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"睇任何一套戲，<br />\n最精髓果 part 係了解套戲表達左咩 message ？<br />\n作為觀眾，又吸收左 d 咩信息，獲得到 d  咩 ？ <br />\n<br />\n我知套野不斷賣弄伏筆呢招，<br />\n令到觀眾不斷睇到「嘩嘩聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」，<br />\n從技術上黎睇，係幾成功，<br />\n至少開頭到中期都取得極大成功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n套巨人真心幾好睇 <br />\n<br />\n但個結果俾到既 message 真心好幼稚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殺自己老母都做得出？<br />\n消滅80%既人又值得？ <br />\n人類大量犧牲就係為左俾始祖尤彌爾睇愛情劇完左個心結？<br />\n睇完用兩個字總結到：<br />\n<br />\n「幼稚」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發覺好多人讚呢套野d 伏筆點好點好，<br />\n根本錯晒 Focus <br />\n套野個 Ending 做得差，<br />\n純綷係因為俾到讀者既 take away message 咁垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a311fd180103be29e82c0240956892811db7ab97","tid":2497051,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:55:35.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"01e03f78aa46550fa916b013bfc1c88d3ed72236","tid":2497051,"uid":375958,"like":1,"dislike":1